('D0160', 'New York State Medicaid', 'prior_auth', 'D0160 Detailed and extensive oral evaluation – problem focused, by report (REPORT NEEDED) A detailed and extensive problem focused evaluation entails extensive diagnostic and cognitive modalities based on the findings of a comprehensive oral evaluation. This information should guide the dentist in the determination of the type of imaging to be used, the frequency of its use, and the number of images to obtain. When ordering a CT, CTA, MRI, MRA, Cardiac Nuclear, or PET procedure an approval number through the Radiology Prior Approval Program is required. Note: The Radiology Prior Approval Program does not include procedure codes D0364-D0368, cone beam computed tomography.', null, null, null, null, null, true, true, null, null, null, 'I. DIAGNOSTIC D0100-D0999', 25, '{"frequency_rule": null, "parser": "heuristic_v1", "source_slug": "nys_medicaid_dental_2026"}'::jsonb, (select id from src)),
